new water treatment and storage facilities.\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1418, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1202, \"end\": 1208, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.748260464730796, \"rank\": 0.2243823366329003, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}, {\"begin\": 1332, \"end\": 1337, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.665999862548737e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"1.4 billion euros\", \"from\": 1232, \"to\": 1249}, {\"ngram\": \"the last decade\", \"from\": 1270, \"to\": 1285}, {\"ngram\": \"the river\", \"from\": 1305, \"to\": 1314}, {\"ngram\": \"new water treatment and storage facilities\", \"from\": 1375, \"to\": 1417}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But major storms still overwhelm the waste water network, some of which dates back to the 19th century, leading to discharges of untreated sewage directly into the river.\", \"from\": 1420, \"to\": 1590, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"major storms\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1436}, {\"ngram\": \"the waste water network\", \"from\": 1453, \"to\": 1476}, {\"ngram\": \"the 19th century\", \"from\": 1506, \"to\": 1522}, {\"ngram\": \"discharges\", \"from\": 1535, \"to\": 1545}, {\"ngram\": \"untreated sewage\", \"from\": 1549, \"to\": 1565}, {\"ngram\": \"the river\", \"from\": 1580, \"to\": 1589}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Test results published last Friday showed levels of E Coli - a bacteria indicating faecal matter - were often twice as high as the maximum permitted limit for Olympic swimming during the week of 10-16 June.\", \"from\": 1592, \"to\": 1798, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Test results\", \"from\": 1592, \"to\": 1604}, {\"ngram\": \